Class OnMultiChoiceClickListenerWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mrapp.android.dialog.listener.AbstractListenerWrapper
      • de.mrapp.android.dialog.listener.OnMultiChoiceClickListenerWrapper

  • public class OnMultiChoiceClickListenerWrapper
extends AbstractListenerWrapper
    A wrapper, which implements the interface OnItemClickListener in order to delegate the method calls to encapsulated listener of the type OnMultiChoiceClickListener.

    • Constructor Detail

      • OnMultiChoiceClickListenerWrapper

        public OnMultiChoiceClickListenerWrapper(OnMultiChoiceClickListener listener,
                                 AlertDialog dialog,
                                 int buttonType)
        Creates a new wrapper, which implements the interface OnItemClickListener in order to delegate the method calls to encapsulated listener of the type OnMultiChoiceClickListener.
        Parameters:
        listener - The listener, which should be encapsulated by the wrapper, as an instance of the type OnMultiChoiceClickListener
        dialog - The dialog, the listener should belong to, as an instance of the class AlertDialog
        buttonType - The type of the button or list item, the listener belongs to, as an Integer value
